{
  "3270430": {
    "name": "Systemic War",
    "steam_appid": 3270430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/ebe4a98fbda0b58d6610f9deb71fbac8.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Systemic War》是一款<strong>现代战略游戏</strong>，你的每一个战略选择都会通过<strong>实时战斗</strong>得到检验，而每一场战斗都会改变持续战争的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择<strong>任意国家</strong>——例如美国、中国、俄罗斯、乌克兰、波兰或土耳其——在动荡的2008–2025年间，逐年带领它走向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/5b4f86bef67843b74d0ec7cb7481aa31.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/5b4f86bef67843b74d0ec7cb7481aa31.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在动态变化的当代世界中管理你的国家，在决策时充分考虑地缘政治的制约条件。请记住，你的每一个选择都可能改变地区甚至全球的力量格局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/353d075d2fae4fd6310bf3ab99c8e48a.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=309 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/3d72580e8e41da8cddc5041152d62055.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在超过25张精心设计的地图上</strong>，你将指挥部队进行动态的实时战斗。战役发生在现实中的关键地点，例如乌克兰的霍斯托梅尔、华沙、阿勒颇、台湾和关岛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在大战略层面上<strong>部署你的军事力量</strong>，将最精锐的部队投入到实时战斗中，决定战争的胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过150种独特的军事单位可供选择</strong>，适应快速变化的现代战场。你可以投资最新的无人机设计、<strong>电子战技术</strong>等最前沿的军事科技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/1f435ba040b406274599a89a8e94afdf.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/1f435ba040b406274599a89a8e94afdf.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/c79546b3d2dd60a2a4d02a26aabd319f.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中没有省份或抽象的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战略地图基于现实中的铁路和公路网络，连接着全球的城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一个真实的基础设施模型，反映了21世纪初的全球变革。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基础设施不仅塑造和平时期的经济，也决定战争时期的后勤与部队机动能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/d998318979e0040753758d2095b2d568.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/d998318979e0040753758d2095b2d568.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/0ed3688e2ff2d4750205b1bac146a617.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过现代 <strong>IS-LM-BP </strong>宏观经济模型管理国家<strong>经济，在利率、GDP和物价之间保持平衡</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定货币政策，控制货币在全球金融市场中的价值，从国际贸易中获利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展工业，决定你的国家是成为资源出口国、半成品制造国，还是高科技供应国。由你来决定国家在全球供应链中的位置，以及在国际市场上的影响力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择你的道路：将国家打造成出口强国、积极对外投资，或通过举债实现社会福利。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/8c45ca701873be1df48b5e736eac19f1.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/8c45ca701873be1df48b5e736eac19f1.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/be95520ce6df28e4559d195ee96948aa.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过150个不同的军事单位被编入真实再现的战术编队</strong>，例如波兰第一华沙装甲旅、美国第三空降旅“拉卡桑斯”、 中国海军陆战队第164旅、土耳其第70机械化旅和俄罗斯第79卫戍机动化步兵团。成为传奇坦克豹2PL、 T-90A，以及AH-64E阿帕奇直升机等航空器和04型、PARS III等步兵战车。运用现代战争中典型的军事单位——<strong>侦察部队、攻击无人机和电子战部队</strong>——为你的坦克和步兵提供支援。在从开阔地到密集城市环境的各种战场上，检验不同部队结构的作战效能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/77f0fa737d747e923fd7bb529f55dcd1.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/77f0fa737d747e923fd7bb529f55dcd1.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/b970948ee3e225cbbea1646802aa61bc.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>参与精选战役，在手工打造的真实场景中展开激战</strong>——这些战火纷飞的战场遍布中东欧、中东及亚太地区。攻占或防守那些你熟悉的真实世界目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Systemic War》重现了全球25个以上重要地点</strong>，包括其标志性建筑和地标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在真实的城市布局、道路和桥梁上指挥部队行动。利用真实地形和自然障碍，在战术上压制对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/bd804ee5af92577923c5cc4be7b52a62.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/bd804ee5af92577923c5cc4be7b52a62.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/bf65192840b3bec240b8d2985ae185fe.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外交的核心在于<strong>冲突升级</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从温和施压到公开战争，每一个决定都会推动局势恶化。使用混合手段削弱对手或争取国际舆论，但要小心：过度的咄咄逼人或羞辱核大国，可能把世界推向核灾难边缘——这意味着游戏结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/b5b2b12b81e44424633eb1ba4e8abe73.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/b5b2b12b81e44424633eb1ba4e8abe73.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/7e40cc794ab240f221d317811124babe.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验当代历史上的关键时刻——无论是真实发生的，还是可能发生的。通过模拟的新闻报道、新闻发布会和现实政治人物的演讲，理解大国竞争如何一步步走向冲突升级。<strong>这里没有冗长的书本或枯燥的讲座，而是一场紧张刺激的沉浸式游戏体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/251bde830716a318890b98aaa0840abb.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/251bde830716a318890b98aaa0840abb.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/8ee9aaf9108cd1e660eba19731de2329.avif?t=1761131011\" width=794 height=119 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建专业<strong>科研团队</strong>，推动军事与民用领域的突破性创新。决定是升级现有武器系统，还是投资下一代革命性原型。别忘了民用科技也很重要——基础设施、能源和物流的提升能增强国家根基。<strong>核心抉择在于：是推动自主研发与本土生产，还是依赖进口与外交？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/11e205a3264a655f4d80355e7c8eeeba.poster.avif?t=1761131011\" width=1170 height=501 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270430/extras/11e205a3264a655f4d80355e7c8eeeba.webm?t=1761131011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
